messageBody:
That's great!  I'm glad to know there's that many people interested in it.

   I was just thinking of an idea.  Wouldn't it be neat if someone would start a small newsletter-type thing in and about Quickscript?  Having it in PDF format on a website would probably be the best way to go, and I know it would be good reading practice for all of us.  I know there's not much in the way of news about Quickscript, so it would be, perhaps, a twice-a-year publication.

   Anyway, I just thought I'd pass that idea on, and see if anyone wants to run with it.  I don't have enough time to put something like this together, but I'd certainly be willing to contribute.

  -Benjamin Bruce
Parker County, Texas
